<div class="contents_text" id="comment_body_2853119"><p>CloudFlareは対応が素早いですね、流石です。<br/>PCI 3.1 and TLS 1.2<br/><a href="https://support.cloudflare.com/hc/en-us/articles/205043158-PCI-3-1-and-TLS-1-2" rel="nofollow" title="cloudflare.com">https://support.cloudflare.com/hc/en-us/articles/205043158-PCI-3-1-and...</a> [cloudflare.com]<br/>&gt; We have implemented a "TLS 1.2-only" flag to allow sites to restrict their content to be served with TLS 1.2 protection only.<br/>&gt; This functionality is currently in testing and will be rolled out to our customers in the upcoming months.</p><p>一方、AzureとAWSはまだ対応を発表していません。<br/>Disable Insecure Ciphers In Azure Websites<br/><a href="http://feedback.azure.com/forums/169385-web-apps-formerly-websites/suggestions/7091994-disable-insecure-ciphers-in-azure-websites" rel="nofollow" title="azure.com">http://feedback.azure.com/forums/169385-web-apps-formerly-websites/sug...</a> [azure.com]<br/>PCI Compliance Protocol Requirements - TLS1.0 Deprecation<br/><a href="https://forums.aws.amazon.com/thread.jspa?messageID=639318" rel="nofollow" title="amazon.com">https://forums.aws.amazon.com/thread.jspa?messageID=639318</a> [amazon.com]</p></div>
